{"tid":437357,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聶德權指《基本法》教育不足　建議增加青年到內地交流、實習機會","createTime":"2017-10-16T02:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T03:32:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0f57522548d504cdb23dd8bade38dea64dd3f8a4","tid":437357,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171016/s00001/5d5dc35add7ba1203336cab0d9e074b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171016%2Fs00001%2F5d5dc35add7ba1203336cab0d9e074b4.jpg&h=d1b24b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局長聶德權今早出席港台節目表示，本港《基本法》教育不足夠，有需要加強。聶德權回應本港青年認為自己是中國人的身份認同愈來愈低，指每人的身份認同都不同，他強調香港是中國國土，「無論如何，我們都是中國人」。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權又指，本港學校要做好憲法及《基本法》教育工作，增加青年到內地交流和實習的機會，開托青年視野，同時政府亦需正視本港與內地的社會矛盾問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171016/s00001/1508119761097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171016%2Fs00001%2F1508119761097&d=oakFjxmgHF0hgzt0QCe%2FC4S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=f730985f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171016%2Fs00001%2F1508119761097&h=59a557e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171016/s00001/1508119761097</a>"},{"pid":"ee2b97289d7b263a8550dd3e3b322b567d37a821","tid":437357,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:51:57.000Z","msg":"基本法教育不足就要返大陸？<br />\n<br />\n我認為條友邏輯不足應該下台"},{"pid":"62764cc357adcc2f06915cf53b5fe5c78fa2eec8","tid":437357,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"增加又點<br />\n<br />\n邊個想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93225d87d7365a516a1fbcf937440bb7ad4432c4","tid":437357,"uid":53379,"like":0